---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---
<MainLayout title="Real-Time Alerts | Spot AI Notifications & Monitoring — Blue Cap IT" description="Spot AI delivers real-time alerts for security incidents, safety violations, and operational anomalies. Custom triggers, instant notifications, and AI-powered event detection across all your cameras.">
  <div class="inner-hero">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <img src="/spotai/spotai-logo.png" alt="Spot AI" style="max-height:50px;width:auto;margin-bottom:1.5rem;"/>
      <div class="crumbs"><a href="index.html">Home</a> <span>/</span> <a href="spotai.html">Spot AI</a> <span>/</span> Real-Time Alerts</div>
      <div class="section-label">Spot AI Platform</div>
      <h1>Real-Time <span class="grad">Alerts</span></h1>
      <p class="section-sub">Stop watching cameras and start responding to events. Spot AI uses AI to detect security incidents, safety violations, and operational anomalies in real time — then sends instant alerts to your team with video clips attached. Custom triggers let you define exactly what matters to your business.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section>
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="why-grid">
        <div>
          <div class="section-label">Proactive Monitoring</div>
          <h2>Your Cameras <span class="grad">Work for You.</span></h2>
          <p class="section-sub">Instead of staff watching live feeds all day, Spot AI's AI does the watching. It detects the events that matter — a person in a restricted area, a vehicle idle too long, a safety violation — and instantly notifies the right people with video evidence attached.</p>
          <div style="margin-top:2rem;display:flex;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap;">
            <a href="contact.html" class="btn-primary">Get a Free Quote</a>
            <a href="tel:4108584031" class="btn-ghost">Call (410) 858-4031</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <ul class="why-list">
          <li class="why-item">
            <div class="why-icon">🔔</div>
            <div><h4>Instant Notifications</h4><p>Get alerts via email, SMS, or mobile app the moment an event is detected — with a video clip attached so you can verify immediately.</p></div>
          </li>
          <li class="why-item">
            <div class="why-icon">⚙️</div>
            <div><h4>Custom Triggers</h4><p>Define your own alert rules — people in restricted zones, vehicles in loading docks after hours, PPE violations, or any custom scenario your business needs.</p></div>
          </li>
          <li class="why-item">
            <div class="why-icon">⚠️</div>
            <div><h4>Safety Monitoring</h4><p>Automatically detect safety violations, slip-and-fall events, and hazardous conditions — helping you prevent injuries before they happen.</p></div>
          </li>
          <li class="why-item">
            <div class="why-icon">📊</div>
            <div><h4>Alert Analytics</h4><p>Track alert frequency, response times, and trends over time. Identify recurring issues and measure the impact of your interventions.</p></div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="section-inner" style="text-align:center;padding:4rem 1.5rem;">
      <h2>Get Alerts That <span class="grad">Actually Matter</span></h2>
      <p class="section-sub" style="max-width:600px;margin:0.8rem auto 2rem;text-align:center;">Contact Blue Cap IT to set up Spot AI real-time alerts for your business. We'll configure custom triggers tailored to your security and operational needs.</p>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:1rem;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;">
        <a href="contact.html" class="btn-primary">Get a Free Quote</a>
        <a href="tel:4108584031" class="btn-ghost">Call (410) 858-4031</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
